# Coordinator spawn budget

Mandatory for **coordinator sessions** only. Full artifact: [private/SPAWN_BUDGET.md](../../private/SPAWN_BUDGET.md). Personal account mode: [coordinator-personal-cost-mode.mdc](./coordinator-personal-cost-mode.mdc).

## Before every spawn

1. Fill the **spawn proposal** in SPAWN_BUDGET (outcome, duration, category S/M/L/XL, ROI H/M/L, files, why not existing agents).
2. **No proposal → no spawn** — except dev-runtime and a single P0 fix-agent when prod/CI is red.
3. Log a row in SPAWN_BUDGET **tracking table** at spawn; close with outcome + ROI when the slot ends.

## Cost categories (pre-spawn estimate)

| Cat | USD |
|-----|-----|
| S | < $5 |
| M | $5–$20 |
| L | $20–$50 |
| XL | > $50 |

## XL gate (all YES)

Business value (P0/P1/roadmap) · no existing agent can do it (WIP≤3, OWNERSHIP) · feature priority over merge queue.

Otherwise split into M/L or defer to Monday checkpoint.

## Defaults

- Small focused agents; one outcome per spawn.
- No large exploratory swarms or parallel explore on the same hot zone.
- WIP≤3 (see [coordinator-v2.mdc](./coordinator-v2.mdc)); one agent per hot zone.

## Pause spawns when

No merge ≥3 days with active agents · no measurable progress ≥48 h on same blocker · On-Demand >$200/week without prod merge · WIP>3.

## Weekly

Roll up spawn counts vs [AI_COST_REPORT.md](../../private/AI_COST_REPORT.md); update ENGINEERING_INTELLIGENCE checkpoint.
